  <span id="freeText14426594203436938083" style="display:none">Is this book perfect? Nope. Did I go completely fan-girl over it. Yep.<br>Stephen Fricking King. You never fail to surprise me.<br>This book did lag in a few spots for me. There was a insta-love going on. I don't give a sheeet.<br><a href="http://imgur.com/uFulmBA" rel="nofollow noopener">
